<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <style>
    body{font-family:Arial,sans-serif;background:#f5f5f5;margin:0;padding:20px}
    .card{background:white;border-radius:12px;max-width:500px;margin:0 auto;overflow:hidden}
    .header{background:#2E7D32;padding:32px;text-align:center}
    .header h1{color:white;margin:0;font-size:22px}
    .body{padding:32px}
    .body h2{color:#2E7D32;margin-top:0}
    .body p{color:#444;line-height:1.6;font-size:15px}
    .info-box{background:#F1F8E9;border-radius:8px;padding:16px;margin:20px 0}
    .info-box p{margin:6px 0;color:#33691E;font-size:14px}
    .badge{background:#FFF9C4;color:#F57F17;padding:6px 14px;
           border-radius:20px;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}
    .footer{padding:20px 32px;border-top:1px solid #eee;
            color:#999;font-size:12px;text-align:center}
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="card">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>🌱 Aguka Smart Farming Kit</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="body">
      <h2>Account Under Review</h2>
      <p>Hello <strong>{{fullName}}</strong>,</p>
      <p>
        Thank you for registering on Aguka Smart Farming Kit.<br>
        <em>Murakoze kwiyandikisha kuri Aguka Smart Farming Kit .</em>
      </p>
      <div class="info-box">
        <p>📋 <strong>Role:</strong> {{role}}</p>
        <p>📱 <strong>Phone:</strong> {{phone}}</p>
        <p>📅 <strong>Date:</strong> {{date}}</p>
      </div>
      <p>
        Your account is <span class="badge">⏳ Under Review</span>
      </p>
      <p>
        Our team will review your details within
        <strong>24 hours</strong>. You will receive
        a confirmation email once approved.<br>
        <em>Konti yawe irimo gusuzumwa. Uzabona ubutumwa kuri 
        imeyili yo kwemeza mu masaha 24.</em>
      </p>
      <p>
        Questions?
        <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}" 
           style="color:#2E7D32">{{supportEmail}}</a>
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      © 2026 Aguka Smart Farming Kit · Rwanda<br>
      This is an automated message.
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
